PATTERNS:
- Converter pattern: Classes take XWPFDocument in constructor, throw IllegalArgumentException for null parameters
- NodeVisitor pattern: Use Flexmark's NodeVisitor with VisitHandler to traverse AST nodes
- Text extraction: Recursive method to extract text from Flexmark AST nodes and children
- Test pattern: Use @TempDir for file IO, @AfterEach for cleanup, assertThrows for exception testing

